We recently noticed some suspicious payments on your Stripe account for Gumroad. For the majority of your payments, our machine learning system provides real-time transaction scoring at the time of a payment, but in some instances, as is the case here, we learn more about a payment's risk level after it's been processed. If you believe these payments were made with a stolen credit card, you should issue a refund to avoid a dispute and the dispute fee.
